title: Series 3000 Ambience Sound Effects
description:
Series 3000 Ambience I Sound Effects Library from Sound Ideas provides you with 200 ambience sound effects available on 12 Audio CDs or as a download. Each ambience track is four minutes long to reduce the need for looping and editing. This royalty free sound effects collection is great for video and film post production. Ambience tracks are provided in the following basic categories: City Atmospheres, Parks, Constructions Sites, Harbors, Jungles, Swamps, Mountains, Deserts, Forests, Countryside, Suburbia, Highways, Airports, Restaurants & Bars, Offices, Room Tones, European Ambiences and Outdoor & Indoor Crowds.
